Trigger → Talent Intake Workflow
   → Bureau check (credit/fraud/dispute)
       → IF freeze/fraud → Verification required
   → IF success → Audit Log → Dashboard → Legacy Broadcast
   → IF failure → Survival Path:
       → Collect Logs → Validate Env → Retry
       → Incident Ticket → Quarantine onboarding
       → Legacy Broadcast → snapshot (ID + error logs)
